  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "A BILL TO AMEND THE SOUTH CAROLINA CODE OF LAWS BY ENACTING \"MADDIE'S LAW\" BY ADDING SECTION 56-5-2915 SO AS TO CREATE THE OFFENSE OF \"RECKLESS DRIVING WITH GREAT BODILY INJURY\" AND TO PROVIDE PENALTIES; AND BY AMENDING SECTION 56-5-2910, RELATING TO RECKLESS VEHICULAR HOMICIDE, SO AS TO INCREASE THE PENALTIES."
    }
  ],
